listing.title: Griffith Wood, Griffith Avenue, Drumcondra, Dublin 9
listing.seoTitle: Griffith Wood, Griffith Avenue, Drumcondra, Dublin 9

prs.location:
Griffith Wood’s location on the longest tree-lined avenue in the Northern Hemisphere is as suited for commuting to and from the city centre as it is for enjoying relaxed suburban living. 

Griffith Wood is located on the prestigious Griffith Avenue, Dublin 9. While quiet and peaceful, the community is a vibrant one that’s well populated by local shops, schools, parks and recreational sporting facilities. All of which are just minutes away and can be reached on foot. 

The complex is also close to Dublin City Centre, Dublin City University, Fairview Park, Croke Park, the International Financial Services Centre (IFSC) and East Point Business Park, and is well serviced by bus and cycle routes. The DART line in Clontarf is a short walk away, while Dublin City Airport and the M1 and M50 motorways can be easily accessed, allowing you to explore Dublin, the counties of Ireland and further afield.

listing.title: Alta Verde, Cross Avenue, Blackrock, Co. Dublin
listing.seoTitle: Alta Verde, Cross Avenue, Blackrock, Co. Dublin

prs.tagLine: Just Launched! Designed for Living, Built for You
prs.location:
Nestled in the heart of Blackrock, Alta Verde on Cross Avenue offers the perfect blend of coastal charm and urban convenience. Ideally situated in South Dublin, it provides seamless access to Dublin City Centre while placing you just minutes from the serenity of the sea and the beauty of the mountains.

With expansive outdoor spaces, beautifully landscaped surroundings, and a vibrant local community, Alta Verde delivers a lifestyle that harmoniously balances nature and connectivity. Excellent transport links — including direct access to the DART (with just a 12-minute journey to Grand Canal Dock) and major bus routes — ensure everything you need is within easy reach, whether it's a coastal stroll, a mountain hike, or a quick commute into the city.

Discover a location that offers the best of both worlds—where modern living meets natural beauty.
